{"tid":1610047,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新魔法師","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:16:56.000Z","uid":105197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c1cfe59ffde3b22665dacb8b852622732cb39d13","tid":1610047,"uid":105197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"火魔法之類雖然已經好多post有配方，<br />\n但可能好多人多嫌麻煩/有困難，<br />\n整唔到火魔法液，更遑論鋁熱彈etc<br />\n但易入手少少嘅，可以係簡簡單單一支通渠水<br />\n個個和理非都擺到落書包帶出嚟戰場<br />\n尤其你喺高位，一拋出去/倒落去就有啲用<br />\n點都好過飛把遮埋去<br />\n<br />\n如果係今日成班人打狗嘅情況，次次用棍打狗佢因為成身裝備，好多時都唔夠傷，但你近距離淋佢，甚至係由下而上潑上去佢塊面，佢一定即時喪失行動能力<br />\n<br />\n通渠水加漂白水個reaction都好猛<br />\n但未諗到室外用法<br />\n<br />\nbtw 火魔法大威力同萬用，係first priority，只係覺得咁樣其他人好過無嘢做到<br />\n<br />\n仲有好危險咖，你班暴徒千祈唔好亂嚟呀<br />\n如果你都覺得危險 <br />\n幫手推推post話俾其他人知唔好做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67bea22eee5cd726eda6cbcd01d81d2401b7409","tid":1610047,"uid":105197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:29:38.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d96e048169b1bf40beaa4baddf88b996cb7a688d","tid":1610047,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"太暴力，不推文了"},{"pid":"cfb50bcf91acf5d347517ff37256528c48a4a9c4","tid":1610047,"uid":105197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"4e260fa8d23a6fd4d45127b038f97b89080a91ad","tid":1610047,"uid":59472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d5f1d64d76429c867946021b33d1947e055e32","tid":1610047,"uid":105197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:35:18.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"e3bcaf37166d59a5a2bc218947dc3aed1e4687af","tid":1610047,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:36:26.000Z","msg":"唔洗戴入場架， 場邊附近好多惠康7仔 ，入面大把貨"},{"pid":"1304896191b